object.text: Welcome, Legend A or D To move and Press SHIFT To run

This is one of the enemies You may jump over it Or kill it (it drops helpful items)
Press left click to attack
Looks like a dead end Or is it?
Secret entrances will always have vegetation at their entrances
This is the key for the portal to end the level

And this is the portal Congratulations!
Press E to open and enter the portal
Items that look like a weapon increase damage by 1
Items that look like a gold chain increase HP by 1 heart
Items that look like a silver chain restore HP by half a heart
This is a wish tree You sacrifice a hearth continer for an item (It can give the key as well) Press E to interact with it
